    dc:description "FIGURE 2. A–D: Gastroserica varians Moser, 1915 (China: Yunnan: Diaolin N.R.); E–H: G. fukiensis Frey, 1972 (Taiwan: Fu Shan). A, E: Aedeagus, left side lateral view; C, G: Aedeagus, right side lateral view; B, F: Parameres, dorsal view; D, H: Habitus (not to scale). Scale: 0.5 mm." ;
