    dc:description "FIGURE 31. Distribution of the genus MoronosericaAhrens, Lukic & Liu, new genus.The unlocalized records of Moronoserica helferi (Bohacz & Ahrens, 2020) and Mor. tenasserimensis (Bohacz & Ahrens, 2020) from Myanmar are not shown here." ;
